    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Check out the <a href=\"https://tips4java.wordpress.com/2011/10/23/drag-layout/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Drag Layout</a>. It is a layout manager designed to allow you to drag components.</p>\n\n<ol>\n<li>if a component is dragged to a negative location then the location of all components are translated by the negative amount to make sure the location of all components is positive</li>\n<li>the preferred size is recalculated after each component is dragged.</li>\n</ol>\n"
